{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to AuraVale, a cozy life sim where your words shape your story. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205530/extras/description_2.png?t=1727998480\" /><strong>Create</strong> <strong>and Care For Your Aura</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Auravale is a life sim where you care for living characters called Aura.  Customize your Aura and watch them come alive as you write their backstory, personality, and quirks in your own words. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205530/extras/serenade.png?t=1727998480\" /><strong>Your words shape your story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Guide your Aura by writing their goals and motivations directly in natural language. Make friends, fall in love, or cause drama - the possibilities are endless! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205530/extras/description_3.png?t=1727998480\" /><strong>Build the perfect home</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize and furnish your home to make it your own. But first, your aura needs a job to earn some cash! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205530/extras/description_4.png?t=1727998480\" /><strong>Invite friends to be your neighbor</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your Aura\u2019s house lives in a cozy town with other Aura.  You can invite your friends to be your neighbor.  After joining, you can visit them and talk to their Aura, even if they are offline.  Need a wingman to join you at the bar? Invite your friend\u2019s Aura for a night on the town!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205530/extras/description_5.png?t=1727998480\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore community-created mods</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">AuraVale was built from the ground up to support modding.  You can directly access UGC  homes, Auras, and even role-playing scenarios directly from the game.  You can even use our no-code modding tools to make your own ~ anything is possible!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205530/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727998480","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205530/page.bg.jpg?t=1727998480","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205530/a1d617c49ace384d78a58745a6d9bbabc33f1dd8/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1727998480","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205530/a1d617c49ace384d78a58745a6d9bbabc33f1dd8/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1727998480","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Captions available","id":13}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to AuraVale, a cozy life sim where your words shape your story. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205530/extras/description_2.png?t=1727998480\" /><strong>Create</strong> <strong>and Care For Your Aura</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Auravale is a life sim where you care for living characters called Aura.  Customize your Aura and watch them come alive as you write their backstory, personality, and quirks in your own words. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https